00:11:51.440 --> 00:11:54.580
at lunch to have
games, and we would

00:11:54.580 --> 00:11:58.020
have near riots over games.

00:11:58.020 --> 00:12:02.390
When you see this girl here, she
had just begun playing chess,

00:12:02.390 --> 00:12:05.310
and then she ended up being
like one of the strongest

00:12:05.310 --> 00:12:06.720
players in the school.

00:12:06.720 --> 00:12:10.750
And I remember at
one point they had--

00:12:10.750 --> 00:12:13.420
