the end of a tournament,

00:12:13.420 --> 00:12:14.610
and there was this boy.

00:12:14.610 --> 00:12:16.650
And then the guys had
kind of come in first,

00:12:16.650 --> 00:12:18.370
and they were all kind
of milling around,

00:12:18.370 --> 00:12:21.470
