in terms of teaching
nonviolence,

00:21:46.110 --> 00:21:48.680
because of all the
rioting and the looting,

00:21:48.680 --> 00:21:52.510
there was a completely
skewed experience of what

00:21:52.510 --> 00:21:54.150
was happening in St. Louis.

00:21:54.150 --> 00:21:57.982
But we were actively
and directly working

00:21:57.982 --> 00:22:00.440
with kids in the hood, helping
them understand nonviolence,

00:22:00.440 --> 00:22:02.180
and they were getting it.

